        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         The exit and entrance have the same mobs. There are 2 types of dogs (whelps and sniffers) and 2 types of sarnaks(underling[sp] and recruit). The later ones are the higher level. For me at 59, the whelps are light blue. I think it's the same at 60. Unless you got Pyre at 60, you will not kill faster than at 59. You will regen mana faster because of Arch Lich .. but killing will not be much faster. IMHO.</P><P>&lt;img src="http://home.t-online.de/home/blueglow/images/iranicus_lotj.jpg" border=0&gt;<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12328" target="_blank">My Gear</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
