        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         FD does not clear the hate list at this level. It does ONLY if you get up from FD AFTER mobs have reached back there spawn spots. If they did, and you still got them both after getting up from FD, then you must've been in aggro range. And if the mob is a roamer, then you most likely never loose aggro. And, of course, if mob has a dot on him, you can bet your ass he wont forget you :)</P><P><font size=1>Iranicus Darkseeker<BR>Level 59 Defiler of Ayonae Ro</font id=size1><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12328" target="_blank">My Gear</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
